Big Brother United Kingdom UK Series 3 Disc 1 of 3  Days 1-30

All of my Big Brother files are archived on 8gb dual layer DVD's and that is how I post them. Once a disc is well seeded I move to the next one. I stated to the person requesting these that if I don't get good help seeding I don't do more series, so please seed as much as you can. 
Thank you!
